name: WiresharkFormatSwitchr
body:
### What is it
支持在当前目录下将tcpdump、nanosecond libpcap、pcapng、nokia tcpdump、redhat tcpdump、snoop2、suse tcpdump格式文件统一转换为NA Sniffer 2.00x 格式文件并输出至当前目录下的output目录。

注：pcapng格式时间戳尚有问题，但并不影响文件在Wireshark中打开。

### Authors and Contributors
In 2016, 仲耀晖 (@tzattack) founded Wireshark Format Switcher.

### Support or Contact
Find me on Twitter and Weibo: @tzattack. My personal website: tzattackblog@wordpress.com
